Package com.flipkart.bean

Class Customer

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.User
com.flipkart.bean.Customer
public class Customer extends User
Represents a Customer in the Flipkart system, extending the User class. This class adds membership details specific to customers who have subscriptions or memberships, enabling the tracking and management of additional customer privileges and access rights based on their membership status.
